snippet.textDisplay: Buddhist music is inspired by Buddhism and Buddhism is a symbol of peace. Buddhist music includes chanting which is the traditional means of preparing the mind for meditation. I did not like this fusion at all because Buddhist music does not fit in here. Hindu and Arabic songs are sung very well by the singers here and the song is nice as well but Aani Chhoying Dolma did not fit in here because her songs are always on the top of all. Every cultural or religious music has its own uniqueness but this song destroyed Buddhist music.
